<h1>China - This Dragon Isn’t Sleeping</h1>
<p><b>Shenzhen, China, April 8, 2014</b> - AsiaInspection, a leading provider of quality control services for businesses importing from Asia, Africa, Southern Europe and Latin America, today announces its 2014 Q1 Barometer, a quarterly synopsis on outsourced manufacturing and the quality control services industry.</p>

